OL,6,FThe disaster and other scandals show
OL,7,Fan "attitude of unaccountable power"
OL,8,Fwhich exists in companies that have
OL,9,F"lost their moral compass", the aunt
OL,10,Fof a 12-year-old girl who died in the
OL,11,Ffire said.
OL,13,FSandra Ruiz called for a change in how
OL,14,Forganisations are led as she addressed
OL,15,Frepresentatives from many of the firms
OL,16,Fwhich bereaved and survivors hold
OL,17,Fresponsible for what happened in June
OL,18,F2017.
