OL,6,FMs Ruiz, whose niece Jessica Urbano
OL,7,FRamirez was among the 72 people killed
OL,8,Fin the blaze, spoke at Grenfell
OL,9,FTestimony Week which began in London
OL,10,Fon Tuesday.
OL,12,FShe was among many to give emotional
OL,13,Ftestimony about those harmed after the
OL,14,FGrenfell Tower fire in 2017.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/12
