OL,6,FThe four-day event is being held as
OL,7,Fpart of an agreement reached following
OL,8,Fthe settlement of a damages claim last
OL,9,Fyear involving about 900 cases and a
OL,10,Fglobal sum of about #150 million in
OL,11,Fcompensation for people affected by
OL,12,Fthe fire.
OL,14,FReferring to the long-running Post
OL,15,FOffice scandal, Ms Ruiz noted that
OL,16,FPaula Vennells, the former boss of
OL,17,Fthat organisation, has agreed to
OL,18,Frelinquish her CBE in the face of a
OL,19,Fpublic outcry following an ITV drama.
