OL,6,FMs Ruiz said: "I ask for any honours
OL,7,Fgiven to parties involved in Grenfell
OL,8,Ffollowing the fire to be withdrawn
OL,9,Funtil the criminal investigation is
OL,10,Fconcluded and, following that,
OL,11,Fpermanently withdrawn for anyone found
OL,12,Fto have failed in their duties and
OL,13,Fresponsibilities."
