OL,6,FArconic, which supplied the cladding
OL,7,Fon the outside of the tower, said it
OL,8,Fhas made a "significant financial
OL,9,Fcontribution to fund the organisation"
OL,10,Fof testimony week, but added that it
OL,11,Fregretted that no representatives
OL,12,Fcould attend.
OL,14,FTo those who were present, Ms Ruiz
OL,15,Fsaid: "You are sitting here because
OL,16,Fyou formed part of this disaster."
OL,18,FListening to the testimonies of
OL,19,Fbereaved and survivors "is the first
OL,20,Fstep in your conciliation process",
OL,21,Fshe said.
