OL,6,FBut she described the fact that not
OL,7,Fall defendant organisations were
OL,8,Fpresent as showing not only "a total
OL,9,Fdisregard for their responsibilities
OL,10,Fbut also a total disregard for our
OL,11,Floss".
OL,13,FShe said the focus for those in
OL,14,Fattendance must be "what you do with
OL,15,Fthe information that you hear and the
OL,16,Fpain that you see", warning it will
OL,17,Fhave been "worthless" if it does not
OL,18,Flead to real change.
