OL,6,FShe said: "If you do not go back to
OL,7,Fyour boardrooms to inspire them to
OL,8,Fmake a commitment to memorialising
OL,9,FGrenfell by making fundamental changes
OL,10,Fin their business models, by putting
OL,11,Fpeople ahead of profits, then this
OL,12,Fwill all have been worthless."
OL,14,FThe Grenfell disaster has shown that
OL,15,F"many organisations, private and
OL,16,Fpublic, have lost their moral
OL,17,Fcompass", Ms Ruiz said.
