OL,6,FShe said an "attitude of unaccountable
OL,7,Fpower" had been "further compounded"
OL,8,Fwith the spotlight falling on other
OL,9,F"miscarriages brought about by similar
OL,10,Fattitudes" such as Windrush, Infected
OL,11,FBlood, and the Post Office.
OL,13,FMs Ruiz said: "We need to see a change
OL,14,Fin how organisations are led."
OL,16,FBereaved father Marcio Gomes, whose
OL,17,Fson Logan was stillborn after the
OL,18,Fblaze, described the life his son
OL,19,Fcould have had.
