OL,6,FSpeaking about missed first milestones
OL,7,Fincluding birthdays and the joy of new
OL,8,Fparenthood, he told the firms: "This
OL,9,Fis what you have taken away from me."
OL,11,FBefore the testimonies began, the
OL,12,Fnames of all those who died in the
OL,13,Ffire were read aloud, followed by a 72-
OL,14,Fsecond silence ` one for each life
OL,15,Flost.
