OL,10,Fchosen not to attend testimony week or
OL,11,Fparticipate in the proceedings" and
OL,12,Fthat there is "anger and a deep sense
OL,13,Fof betrayal in the way this event has
OL,14,Fcome about".
OL,16,FIt said: "It has caused tremendous
OL,17,Fhurt and harm for those who should be
